        <h1 class="govuk-heading-xl">
            Privacy
        </h1>
        <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">How we use your personal information</h2>
        <p>The manage apprenticeships service is run by the Education and Skills Funding Agency (ESFA), an executive agency of the Department for Education (DfE).</p>
        <p>This privacy notice explains how we (<abbr title="Department for Education">DfE</abbr> and <abbr title="Education and Skills Funding Agency">ESFA</abbr>) use your personal information.</p>
        <p>For the purposes of relevant data protection legislation, DfE is the data controller for personal information it processes, so that it can carry out its functions.</p>
        <p>Where you register on the service the personal information you give us will be used for administration and research purposes.</p>
        <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">How long we hold personal information</h2>
        <p>We'll retain the personal information for administration purposes only for as long as necessary. Personal data required for research purposes may be retained indefinitely.</p>
        <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">Who we share your personal information with</h2>
        <p>We may share your information where the law allows it to enable the running of the manage apprenticeships service, or where we have a legal obligation to do so.</p>
        <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">Your individual rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
            <li>request a copy of personal information that we hold about you</li>
            <li>request that we correct any wrong or incomplete personal information</li>
        </ul>
        <p>You can access the information we hold on you by signing in to your account.</p>
        <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">How to complain</h2>
        <p>Contact us using our <a href="https://www.education.gov.uk/contactus/efa" class="govuk-link" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">secure online contact form</a> or by writing to:</p>
        <p>
            Ministerial and Public Communications Division<br>
            Department for Education<br>
            Piccadilly Gate Store Street<br>
            Manchester<br>
            M1 2WD
        </p>
        <p>If you wish to contact the DfE's data protection officer, please use the secure online form or write to the address above.</p>
        <p>You also have the right to complain to the <a href="https://ico.org.uk/concerns/" class="govuk-link" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Information Commissioner's Office</a>.</p>
